main event: Three witnesses in Springdale, Ohio observed five bright, hovering UFOs organized in a line on the horizon on August 5, 1966.
interesting points: The UFOs would go on and off, blinking for about a minute.
The UFOs hovered and maneuvered in a line for about 15 minutes.
The objects were described as very bright and hovering.
One witness said the objects looked like the 'space ship on TV'.
The UFOs were estimated to be about 300 feet across.
sighted object: five bright, hovering UFOs in a line formation
